[normal]1.5
[normal] 
[normal]              
[normal]I
[normal]n order to reduce the number of collisions on the roads within Greater Manchester 
[normal]officers above
[normal] from Traffic Network Section developed an innovative approach named Operation 
[normal]‘
[normal]Grimaldi
[normal]’
[normal] which underpins 
[normal]the force
[normal] road saf
[normal]ety initiative Operation 
[normal]‘
[normal]Dice
