[normal].2  
[normal]              
[normal]The HGV 
[normal]unit and 
[normal]articulated 
[normal]trailer 
[normal]is set at a slight angle as though 
[normal]the driver / vehicle was 
[normal]turning
[normal] left (the most common 
[normal]manoeuvre
[normal] 
[normal]involved in
[normal] KSI’s)
[normal] to highlight the blind 
[normal]spots
[normal].
[normal] 
[normal]A member of the public then
[normal] sits in the driver’s seat 
[normal]where 
[normal]t
[normal]he trainer 
[normal]p
[normal]oint
[normal]s
[normal] out the 
