[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3
[normal].3
[normal]              
[normal]This also 
[normal]dispels 
[normal]the 
[normal]assumption 
[normal]that they can see the drivers mirror so 
[normal]the driver
[normal] must be able to see them. 
[normal]Th
[normal]e input 
